title: Aynur - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Aynur performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 24, 2023.

Songs:
Berfek Barî - Lure Lure
Rewend (Göçebe)
Qumrikê
Malan Barkir-Bêrîvanê
Hedûr

Aynur Doğan - Tembur / Vocals
Kevin Hays - Piano
Ismail Lumanowski - Clarinet
Ilkin Deniz - Bass
Jean Christophe Leroy - Drums

Host: Darek Mazzone
Audio Engineers: Julian Martlew & Kevin Suggs
Audio Mixing: Kevin Suggs
Audio Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro & Kendall Rock
Editor: Jim Beckmann

https://aynurdogan.net
